INSERT INTO execution_metrics (
  execution_id,
  workflow_id,
  workflow_name,
  workflow_version,
  n8n_version,
  environment,
  status,
  started_at,
  owner_id
) VALUES (
  $1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, NOW(), $8
);

INSERT INTO n8n_schedule_tracking (
  field,
  value,
  created_at,
  execution_id,
  unique_id,
  ativo
)
VALUES (
  $1, $2, NOW(), $3, $4, $5
)
ON CONFLICT (unique_id) DO UPDATE
SET
  field = EXCLUDED.field,
  value = EXCLUDED.value,
  created_at = NOW(),
  execution_id = EXCLUDED.execution_id,
  ativo = EXCLUDED.ativo;
